---

<aside class="anti-copy" role="note">
  <span class="icon" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="1.2rem" height="1.2rem">
      <path d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.25 3.75 10.15 9 11.25C17.25 21.15 21 16.25 21 11V5L12 1z"/>
      <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4" fill="none" stroke="rgba(7,23,53,0.8)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>
  </span>
  <div class="body">
    <p class="primary">Los datos se habilitan al confirmar tu carton.</p>
    <p class="hint">Sistema anti-copia activo. Tu progreso es personal e intransferible.</p>
  </div>
</aside>

<style>
  .anti-copy {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 0.85rem;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.2rem;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 0.85rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pm-blue-700, #1749d8), var(--pm-blue-900, #071735));
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(7, 23, 53, 0.32);
  }

  .icon {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    width: 2.4rem;
    height: 2.4rem;
    border-radius: 0.65rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    color: var(--pm-white);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .body {
    display: flex;
    min-width: 0;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.1rem;
  }

  .primary {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--pm-white);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 850;
  }

  .hint {
    margin: 0;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
</style>
